981論文研討(碩一B)









　



 








　









　






課程名稱：論文研討(一)B組  
		==> 行銷研究領域


必選修：企碩一，2學分，必修


課程目標與簡介：

培養研究生對學術論文之閱讀、簡報與評析之能力，使其對研究本質有初步之認識，以及對不同領域研究課題之瞭解，以助其在未來進行學術論文之撰寫。


課程簡介：

由授課教師指定相關領域之學術期刊論文。

行銷管理領域：
PRICING
1. Incidental Prices and Their Effect on Willingness to Pay, JM, 2004.

2. Penny 
		Wise and Pound Foolish: The Left-Digit Effect in Price Cognition, JCR, 
		2005.


CONSUMER CHOICE

3. Choice 
		Construction Versus Preference Construction: The Instability of 
		Preferences Learned in Context, JMR, 2008.

4. Compromise and Attraction Effects under Prevention and Promotion 
		Motivations, JCR, 2007


MATERIALISM

5. Self-control for the Righteous: Toward a Theory of Precommitment to 
		Indulgence, JCR, 2002.

6. The 
		Material Values Scale: Measurement Properties and Development of a Short 
		Form, JCR, 2004.


MENTAL ACCOUNTING

7. Upgrades and New Purchases, JM, 2006.

8. Can 
		Trade-ins Hurt You? Exploring the effect of a Trade-in on Consumers’ 
		Willingness to Pay for a New Product, JMR, 2008.


CONSTRUAL LEVEL THEORY (CLT)

9. Construal Level Theory and Consumer Behavior, JCP, 2007; Seeing the 
		Forest or the Trees: Implications of Construal Level Theory for Consumer 
		Choice, JCP, 2007.


MEMORY

10. 
		Pattern of Affect reactions to Advertisements the Integration of 
		Moment-to-Moment Responses Into Overall Judgments, JMR, 1997.

11. Social 
		Context and Advertising Memory, JMR, 2007.


REGULATORY FOCUS

12. When 
		More May Be Less: The Effects of Regulatory Focus on Responses to 
		Different Comparative Frames, JCR, 2006.

13. 
		Understanding Impulsive Eaters' Choice Behavior: The Motivational 
		Influences of Regulatory Focus, JMR, 2007.


VARIETY SEEKING

14. The 
		Impact of Private versus Public Consumption on Variety-Seeking Behavior, 
		JCR, 2002.

15. 
		Variety Seeking Tendency in Choice for Others-Interpersonal and 
		Intrapersonal Causes, JCR, 2006.


JUSTIFICATION

16. 
		Justification Effects on Consumer Choice of Hedonic and Utilitarian 
		Goods, JMR, 2005.

17. Jack 
		of All Trades or Master of One, JCR, 2007.


REFERENCE PRICE

18. 
		Broadening the Scope of Reference Price Advertising Research: A Field 
		Study of Consumer Shopping Involvement, JM, 2006.

19. Cents 
		or Percent? The Effects of Promotion Framing on Price Expectations and 
		Choice, JM, 2007.


RELATIONSHIP

20. The 
		Difference between Communal and Exchange Relationships, PSPB, 1993.

21. Impact 
		of Desired Relationship Type on Affective Reactions to Choosing and 
		Being Required to Help, PSPB, 1992.


COMPROMISE EFFECT

22. The 
		Impact of a product’s country-of-origin on compromise and attraction 
		effects, ML, 2007

23. 
		Information Format-Option Compatibility and the Compromise Effect, P&M, 
		2008


BUNDLE

24. The 
		Influence of Price Discount Framing on the Evaluation of a Product 
		Bundle, JCR, 2004

25. 
		Shopper Response to Bundle Promotions for Package Goods, JMR, 2007


成績評量：



出席     10%


報告     
			40%


評論     
			25%


心得     25%



進度表：
9/17    
		課程簡介、讀文獻做研究




 


